precis:
REPORT ON THE STATE OF CANADA'S FORESTS REGULATIONS which maintains the
legal requirement (replaces section 7 of the repealed Department of
Forestry Act) for the Minister to prepare an annual report respecting the
state of the forests in Canada and their contribution to the economy and
environment and to the social well-being of Canadians.
